    <div class="container vanta-bg-event">
        <br><br>
        <header class="header">
            <h1> ALGOCODE </h1>
            <marquee class="marqueedesk" behavior="" direction="">Co/de and Conquer</marquee>
            <p class="marqueemob"> Co/de and Conquer </p>
            <p class="para-indent">We present you with yet another excuse to code your brain and heart out - ALGOCODE.
